# Screenshots folder for E2E testing evidence

This folder stores test screenshots captured during cross-browser and responsive design testing:
- 1024px width renders (Chrome, Edge, Safari)
- 1920px width renders (Chrome, Edge, Safari)
- Error state screenshots
- PowerPoint integration validation screenshots

Naming convention: `{user_story}_{browser}_{width}_{state}.png`
Example: `US1_Chrome_1920px_valid.png`